@startuml
[*] --> PowerOn
PowerOn --> [*]
PowerOn --> Startup
Startup --> Ready : everything is fine
Ready --> Reset : reset button pressed
Ready --> Activate : activate button pressed
Ready --> Deactivate : deactivate button pressed
Ready --> Monitoring : activate button pressed
Monitoring --> Alarm : sensor triggered
Alarm --> Monitoring : false alarm or time ended
Monitoring --> Deactivate : deactivate button pressed
Ready --> PowerOff : power off button pressed
PowerOff --> [*]
@enduml
